{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"654","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"元大金攜供應商 建構綠色供應鏈","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>04:10 2020/03/13 </span><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>工商時報 謝奇璋</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/CSR%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 367px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>元大金控舉辦<span lang='EN-US'>2020</span>供應商<span lang='EN-US'>CSR</span>大會。圖／元大金控提供</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>元大金控致力推動企業永續發展，除自身落實企業社會責任，也要求供應商夥伴共同履行，連續兩年召開供應商大會，今年有<span lang='EN-US'>80</span>家主要供應商參與，會中安排安永聯合會計師事務所講師分享供應鏈管理與永續採購，邀請供應商夥伴一起實踐永續經營的願景與承諾。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>為推動供應商實踐企業社會責任，自<span lang='EN-US'>2015</span>年<span lang='EN-US'>11</span>月起，針對集團內各公司主要往來供應商，要求於採購合約內增列「企業社會責任條款」或簽署「人權及環境永續條款承諾書」，完成率達<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>％，明訂供應商應履行及遵守各項勞動條件、環境保護及勞動人權等法令規範。　此外，也針對供應商屬性，視其對勞動條件、職業安全衛生、環境保護及勞動人權各面向的衝擊程度，加強管理。<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年向主要供應商進行人權盡職調查，目前進行永續採購指南（<span lang='EN-US'>ISO 20400</span>）認證流程，期以永續管理方法導入採購規範，建置完善「永續採購流程」。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>元大金控透過採購及業務配合，向供應商推廣環境永續及綠色消費的觀念，建構更廣大的綠色消費市場。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源：</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20200313000518-260210?chdtv</span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-03-16","clk_count":"120"}},"__N_SSG":true}